:"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"also named “RGAA”.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"See for example ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","type":"reference"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio","kind":"symbol"}}}